  "detailed_description": "You're being chased by the enemy and have to escape.<br>Fight their drones, turrets and vehicles on a train through several levels and several waves.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/477120/extras/2f5d29dcca26152657892cbc530c3b12.poster.avif?t=1764347466\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/477120/extras/2f5d29dcca26152657892cbc530c3b12.webm?t=1764347466\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/477120/extras/2f5d29dcca26152657892cbc530c3b12.mp4?t=1764347466\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>You can choose between the Story or the Wave Mode. In Story Mode, you have to go through multiple level after another and defeat the end bosses in each level.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/477120/extras/3128de59dddebbc09df62fce015c8ec9.poster.avif?t=1764347466\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/477120/extras/3128de59dddebbc09df62fce015c8ec9.webm?t=1764347466\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/477120/extras/3128de59dddebbc09df62fce015c8ec9.mp4?t=1764347466\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>In the Wave Mode, you encounter waves of enemies and during a pause, you can buy new weapons.<br><br>Use different types of weapons to deal as much as damage with the least amount of bullets. <br>You can pick between a pistol, a shotgun, a machine gun and a grenade launcher.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/477120/extras/013d171f7ff313d441bc138d19e03705.poster.avif?t=1764347466\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/477120/extras/013d171f7ff313d441bc138d19e03705.webm?t=1764347466\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/477120/extras/013d171f7ff313d441bc138d19e03705.mp4?t=1764347466\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Dodge their attacks during the bullet time.<br>The bullet time activates as soon as a enemy bullet gets close, dodge it by physically moving in the room while the time is slowed down.",
  "about_the_game": "You're being chased by the enemy and have to escape.<br>Fight their drones, turrets and vehicles on a train through several levels and several waves.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/477120/extras/2f5d29dcca26152657892cbc530c3b12.poster.avif?t=1764347466\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/477120/extras/2f5d29dcca26152657892cbc530c3b12.webm?t=1764347466\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/477120/extras/2f5d29dcca26152657892cbc530c3b12.mp4?t=1764347466\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>You can choose between the Story or the Wave Mode. In Story Mode, you have to go through multiple level after another and defeat the end bosses in each level.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/477120/extras/3128de59dddebbc09df62fce015c8ec9.poster.avif?t=1764347466\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/477120/extras/3128de59dddebbc09df62fce015c8ec9.webm?t=1764347466\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/477120/extras/3128de59dddebbc09df62fce015c8ec9.mp4?t=1764347466\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>In the Wave Mode, you encounter waves of enemies and during a pause, you can buy new weapons.<br><br>Use different types of weapons to deal as much as damage with the least amount of bullets. <br>You can pick between a pistol, a shotgun, a machine gun and a grenade launcher.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/477120/extras/013d171f7ff313d441bc138d19e03705.poster.avif?t=1764347466\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/477120/extras/013d171f7ff313d441bc138d19e03705.webm?t=1764347466\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/477120/extras/013d171f7ff313d441bc138d19e03705.mp4?t=1764347466\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Dodge their attacks during the bullet time.<br>The bullet time activates as soon as a enemy bullet gets close, dodge it by physically moving in the room while the time is slowed down.",
